headline: Raymond James Sees Market Cooling but These 2 Stocks Still Look Like Buys
summary: Markets appear to be in retreat mode, pulling back from the record highs notched in late October. Even with the six-week government shutdown now over and federal agencies reopening, the initial sense of relief proved short-lived. Investors shifted to a more cautious stance as questions resurfaced about whether valuations have moved ahead of fundamentals and how the Federal Reserve will approach its next policy decisions.
